        dots[i].classList.remove("active");
    }

    // Increment slide index and reset if exceeds length
    slideIndex++;
    if (slideIndex > slides.length) {
        slideIndex = 1;
    }

    // Display the current slide and set the corresponding dot as active
    slides[slideIndex - 1].style.display = "block";
    dots[slideIndex - 1].classList.add("active");

    // Call showSlides function again after 3 seconds (adjust as needed)
    setTimeout(showSlides, 3000); // Change image every 3 seconds
}

// Optional: Add functionality for clicking on dots to navigate
let dots = document.getElementsByClassName("dot");
for (let i = 0; i < dots.length; i++) {
    dots[i].onclick = function() {
        slideIndex = i + 1;
        showSlides();
    }
}
</script>
